message.content:
1. 17 patients were enrolled in the study.
2. All 17 patients were treated with GEM-CAP.
3. 13 patients achieved disease control after being treated with GEM-CAP.
4. The 13 patients who achieved disease control were randomised into two groups.
5. 7 patients were randomised to arm A.
6. 6 patients were randomised to arm B.
